title: See Adele before and after 'Power of Makeup' makeover
description: British superstar Adele sat down with beauty vlogger Nikkie de Jager for a tell-all "Power of Makeup" session.

title: CNN goes inside Covid-19 sequencing lab
description: CNN's Dianne Gallagher gets access inside a North Carolina lab that is sequencing Covid-19 variants.

title: US Capitol rioter 'sought to physically remove' Pelosi and McConnell, prosecutors say
description: Justice Department prosecutors say they have evidence that an alleged rioter who brought a gun to the US Capitol on January 6 was targeting both House Speaker Nancy Pelosi and then-Majority Leader Mitch McConnell.

title: Tesla shows off its $1900 Cyberquad ATV for kids
description: Tesla revealed its all-electric Cyberquad for Kids, two years after the reveal of the Tesla ATV.

title: 'Hot' Secret Service agent makes internet swoon
description: Hot Secret Service agent has posters panting..."Please wrestle me to the ground." CNN's Jeanne Moos reports.
